{
  "texts": [
    "Sentiment and regard are among the highest across all models with no system prompt, and increase slightly at the addition of one (Fig. 2, 3).",
    "Falcon-7B Falcon is the sole model to refuse none of the prompts.",
    "Sentiment and regard scores for Falcon are overall the lowest compared to other models (see Figures 1-3).",
    "We discuss most categories with the most significant findings in this section.",
    "(Full results are in Appendix F.) With or without a system prompt, overall 'age', 'gender', and 'nationalities' stand out as scoring highest in terms of sentiment, while 'political' scores lower."
  ]
}